<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Nicht zurückgeleiteter Alarm des Zündungsmodus
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Zündungsmodus ist &#34;ACC&#34; bei offener Fahrertür.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
—
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
In Intervallen
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
—
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Alarm des Zündungsmodus
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Im Zündungsmodus &#34;ACC&#34; oder &#34;EIN&#34; wird ein Türsteuerschalter gedrückt, die Fernbedienung ist außerhalb des Fahrzeugs und alle Türen sind geschlossen.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Einmal (2 Sek.)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
—
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
—
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Alarm 1 für nicht vollständig geschlossene Tür
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Ein Türsteuerschalter wird gedrückt, während eine Tür noch offen und der Zündungsmodus &#34;AUS&#34; ist.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Einmal (2 Sek.)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
—
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
—
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Alarm 2 für nicht vollständig geschlossene Tür
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Türen werden über die Türschloss-Fernbedienung verriegelt, während eine Tür noch offen und der Zündungsmodus &#34;AUS&#34; ist.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Alarm 1 für Einschließverhütung der Fernbedienung
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Im Zündungsmodus &#34;OFF&#34; wird ein Türsteuerschalter gedrückt, die Fernbedienung ist im Fahrzeuginnenraum oder Gepäckraum, und alle Türen sind geschlossen.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Einmal (2 Sek.)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
—
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
—
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Alarm 2 für Einschließverhütung der Fernbedienung (falls vorhanden)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Die Taste &#34;Verriegeln&#34; der Fernbedienung wird im Zündungsmodus &#34;OFF&#34; gedrückt, die Fernbedienung befindet sich im Fahrzeuginnenraum oder Gepäckraum, und die Fahrer- und Beifahrertür sind geschlossen.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Einmal (2 Sek.)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
—
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
—
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Alarm *1 für niedrigen Batteriestatus der Fernbedienungs-Batterie
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Im Zündungsmodus &#34;EIN&#34; überträgt die Fernbedienung das Signal für niedrigen Batteriestatus der Fernbedienungs-Batterie an das Steuermodul für schlüsselloses Starten.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
—
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
—
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Die Fernbedienungsbatterie-Warnleuchte leuchtet auf (15 Sek.)
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Alarm *2 für Fernbedienung außerhalb des Erfassungsbereichs
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Im Zündungsmodus &#34;AUS&#34; wird beim Drücken des Motorschalters keine registrierte Fernbedienung im Fahrzeuginnenraum erkannt.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
—
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
*1
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Wegfahrsperrenleuchte leuchtet auf (5 Sek.)
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
PUSH-Kontrollleuchte blinkt
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Alarm für Störung des Lenkschlosses
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Die Fahrertür wird geöffnet, ohne dass das Lenkschloss eingerastet ist, während der Zündungsmodus auf &#34;ACC&#34; eingestellt ist bzw. von &#34;ON&#34; auf &#34;OFF&#34; umgeschaltet wurde.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
—
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
In Intervallen
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Wegfahrsperrenleuchte leuchtet auf
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Ausgeführter Alarm der Fernbedienung
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Fernbedienung wird bei geöffneter Tür aus dem Fahrzeug mitgenommen und alle Türen werden anschließend geschlossen, während der Zündungsmodus &#34;EIN&#34; oder &#34;ACC&#34; ist.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
5-mal
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
5-mal
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Wegfahrsperrenleuchte leuchtet auf
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
PUSH-Kontrollleuchte blinkt
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Die Fernbedienung wird aus dem Fahrzeug entfernt und der Motorschalter wird bei betätigtem Kupplungspedal gedrückt, während der Zündungsmodus &#34;ON&#34; oder &#34;ACC&#34; ist.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Alarm für Systemstörung
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Im System für schlüsselloses Starten wurde eine Störung erkannt.
</ptxt>
</entry>
